
<view style="text-align:center;margin:10px 100px 30px 100px">
<image style="width:100px;height:100px;border-radius:100px"src="{{github_src}}"></image>
<text style="line-height:20px;width:200px;font-size:10pt">
GitHub 是一个面向开源及私有软件项目的托管平台，因为只支持 Git 作为唯一的版本库格式进行托管，故名 GitHub。
</text>
</view>

<view style="margin:10px 20px 20px 20px;border:1px solid #A8A8A8;border-radius:5px" hidden="{{ hidden_login}}">
<view style="height:40px;background:#FAFAFA;border-bottom: #A8A8A8 solid 0.1px;border-top-left-radius:5px;border-top-right-radius:5px">
<view style="height:40px;margin-left:10px;display: table-cell;vertical-align:middle">
<text style="margin-left:10px;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold">Sign in to Github</text>
</view>

</view>
<view style="margin-left:10px;margin-top:10px;text-align:left">
<view>
<text style="font-size:10pt">Username or email</text>
</view>
<view style="margin-top:5px">
<input  bindinput="username" style="border:1px solid #A8A8A8;margin-right:10px;border-radius:5px" />
</view>

<view style="margin-top:10px">
<text style="font-size:10pt">Password</text>
</view>
<view style="margin-top:5px">
<input  bindinput="password" style="border:1px solid #A8A8A8;margin-right:10px;border-radius:5px" />
</view>
<button style="margin-right:10px;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:10px;height:30px;border-radius:1px;font-size:10pt" catchtap="signIn">Sign in</button>
</view>
</view>

  <view class="body-view">
    <loading hidden="{{hidden}}" bindchange="loadingChange">
      登录中...
    </loading>
  </view>